# VIVE Wave SDK

VIVE Wave is an open platform and toolset that enables easy Mobile VR content development and high-performance device optimization for third party partners. The VIVE Wave VR SDK offers an open interface enabling interoperability between numerous mobile VR headsets and accessories such as the Vive Focus. This allows players with different VR devices an easy access pathway to your content.

See VIVE Wave SDK Developer Guide for further information:
https://hub.vive.com/storage/docs/en-us/